 idiots..."</li><li> "I'm giving them a free show for free!"</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DespairEventHorizon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DespairEventHorizon">Despair Event Horizon</a>:<ul><li> The faux cancellation of the show at the end of February 2012 was this for many trolls, until Ghost returned.</li><li> And then those regular shows would be abruptly cut off by the <em>actual</em> cancellation of the show on May 24th.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DirtyOldMan" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DirtyOldMan">Dirty Old Man</a>: Ghost's "Uncle Bernie" impression is this by default. Then the ensuing splices featuring him take this <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UpToEleven" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UpToEleven">Up to Eleven</a>, only they're usually about <em>Ghost</em> being a sexual deviant instead.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DisproportionateRetribution" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DisproportionateRetribution">Disproportionate Retribution</a>:<ul><li> On 9/29/11, a caller simply said "Fuck you". Ghost decided to harass that caller by calling him back repeatedly, then leaves a message on the phone hoping his mother hears, and even lies and says the caller traumatized his <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RetCon" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RetCon">dead</a> grandmother.</li><li> Ghost's reaction to CelticBrony trying to dox him was to not only dox him back, but to dox any trolls connected with him and run them off the internet, then encourage Celtic to commit suicide.</li><li> A caller who made a pizzagate joke had his number said on the air, which was followed by trolls doxing him within minutes after the show ended.</li><li> Trumping Capitalist, one of Ghost's long time fans, had annoyed Inner Circle members in the chatroom and was banned. Following this, and him attacking the Inner Circle, his parents 